Text: Re EFCU QuickTeller Phone Service Unavailable This SundayFederal Credit Union From Enron Federal Credit NRON on PM CDT Sent by Enron NRON To All Enron Worldwide cc Subject EFCU QuickTeller Phone Service Unavailable This Sunday Due to communication equipment upgrades by Enron QuickTeller Enron Federal Credit Unions Automated Phone Account Service will be unavailable Sunday October st from am to pm If you need access to your credit union accounts QuickLink PC Banking is available through our web site at wwwefcuenroncom If you are not yet set up for QuickLink access please send us an email and we will be glad to get you set up We apologize for any inconvenience Thank you
